<pre>"Days fly-by & time passes; But in this hectic life, you are and will always remain close to our hearts."
Every one enters the gates of JUIT with some dreams, and some day will leave the university with a sense of nostalgia, a place we call home for all the years spent here.
Graduation isn't the end. It's the beginning. And to start this chapter, an Alumni Affairs Committee is set up. Alumni Affairs Committee is a student body that aims to foster and bridge the interaction between the University and its Alumni because "You can take a JUITian out of JUIT but not JUIT out of a JUITian". With this motto in mind, our aim is to organize and publicize alumni events, batch reunions, maintain alumni database and find lost souls (alumni with whom we have completely lost contact).</pre>